lead_paragraph: Akrum Wadley ran for 121 yards and two touchdowns, LeShun Daniels added 83 yards rushing and two scores, and No. 17 Iowa beats Miami (Ohio) 45-21 on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Wadley Runs No. 17 Iowa to 45-21 Win Over Miami (Ohio)
